Exclude action registrations by pattern from product.json

Adds pattern-based filtering to registerAction2 and MenuRegistry.appendMenuItem.
Actions whose command ID matches a prefix in product.json excludedActionPatterns
are silently dropped — no command, menu entry, or keybinding is registered.
